<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<ui version="4.0">
 <class>DemToTactileDialogBase</class>
 <widget class="QDialog" name="DemToTactileDialogBase">
  <property name="geometry">
   <rect>
    <x>0</x>
    <y>0</y>
    <width>550</width>
    <height>480</height>
   </rect>
  </property>
  <property name="windowTitle">
   <string>DEM to Tactile 3D</string>
  </property>
  <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="verticalLayout">
   <item>
    <widget class="QTabWidget" name="tabWidget">
     <property name="currentIndex">
      <number>0</number>
     </property>
     <widget class="QWidget" name="tabTerrain">
      <attribute name="title">
       <string>1. Relevo (DEM)</string>
      </attribute>
      <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="verticalLayout_2">
       <item>
        <layout class="QFormLayout" name="formLayout">
         <item row="0" column="0">
          <widget class="QLabel" name="label">
           <property name="text">
            <string>Camada Raster (MDE):</string>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="0" column="1">
          <widget class="QgsMapLayerComboBox" name="mRasterLayerComboBox"/>
         </item>
         <item row="1" column="0">
          <widget class="QLabel" name="label_2">
           <property name="text">
            <string>Largura do Modelo (mm):</string>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="1" column="1">
          <widget class="QDoubleSpinBox" name="mWidthSpinBox">
           <property name="minimum">
            <double>10.0</double>
           </property>
           <property name="maximum">
            <double>2000.0</double>
           </property>
           <property name="value">
            <double>150.0</double>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="2" column="0">
          <widget class="QLabel" name="label_3">
           <property name="text">
            <string>Altura do Modelo (mm):</string>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="2" column="1">
          <widget class="QDoubleSpinBox" name="mHeightSpinBox">
           <property name="minimum">
            <double>10.0</double>
           </property>
           <property name="maximum">
            <double>2000.0</double>
           </property>
           <property name="value">
            <double>150.0</double>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="3" column="0">
          <widget class="QLabel" name="label_4">
           <property name="text">
            <string>Resolução do Modelo (mm/pixel):</string>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="3" column="1">
          <widget class="QDoubleSpinBox" name="mResSpinBox">
           <property name="singleStep">
            <double>0.1</double>
           </property>
           <property name="value">
            <double>0.5</double>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="4" column="0">
          <widget class="QLabel" name="label_5">
           <property name="text">
            <string>Altura da Base (cota m):</string>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="4" column="1">
          <widget class="QDoubleSpinBox" name="mBaseHeightSpinBox">
           <property name="minimum">
            <double>-10000.0</double>
           </property>
           <property name="maximum">
            <double>10000.0</double>
           </property>
           <property name="value">
            <double>0.0</double>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="5" column="0">
          <widget class="QLabel" name="label_6">
           <property name="text">
            <string>Exagero Vertical:</string>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="5" column="1">
          <widget class="QDoubleSpinBox" name="mExaggerationSpinBox">
           <property name="minimum">
            <double>0.1</double>
           </property>
           <property name="value">
            <double>1.5</double>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
        </layout>
       </item>
       <item>
        <widget class="QGroupBox" name="mExtentGroupBox">
         <property name="title">
          <string>Extensão de Recorte do Relevo</string>
         </property>
         <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="verticalLayout_4">
          <item>
           <widget class="QgsExtentWidget" name="mExtentWidget"/>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </widget>
       </item>
      </layout>
     </widget>
     <widget class="QWidget" name="tabVectors">
      <attribute name="title">
       <string>2. Vetores (Linhas e Polígonos / Lagos)</string>
      </attribute>
      <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="verticalLayout_3">
       <item>
        <widget class="QLabel" name="label_7">
         <property name="text">
          <string>Adicione camadas vetoriais (linhas como trilhas/rios ou polígonos como lagos/lagoas):</string>
         </property>
        </widget>
       </item>
       <item>
        <widget class="QTableWidget" name="mVectorTable">
         <property name="columnCount">
          <number>4</number>
         </property>
         <column>
          <property name="text">
           <string>Camada Vetorial</string>
          </property>
         </column>
         <column>
          <property name="text">
           <string>Efeito Tátil</string>
          </property>
         </column>
         <column>
          <property name="text">
           <string>Buffer (Metros)</string>
          </property>
         </column>
         <column>
          <property name="text">
           <string>Altura/Prof. (mm)</string>
          </property>
         </column>
        </widget>
       </item>
       <item>
        <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="horizontalLayout_2">
         <item>
          <widget class="QPushButton" name="mAddVectorButton">
           <property name="text">
            <string>Adicionar Camada</string>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item>
          <widget class="QPushButton" name="mRemoveVectorButton">
           <property name="text">
            <string>Remover Selecionada</string>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
        </layout>
       </item>
      </layout>
     </widget>
     <widget class="QWidget" name="tabExport">
      <attribute name="title">
       <string>3. Exportar (STL)</string>
      </attribute>
      <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="verticalLayout_5">
       <item>
        <layout class="QFormLayout" name="formLayout_2">
         <item row="0" column="0">
          <widget class="QLabel" name="label_8">
           <property name="text">
            <string>Salvar Arquivo STL em:</string>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
         <item row="0" column="1">
          <widget class="QgsFileWidget" name="mFileWidget">
           <property name="dialogTitle">
            <string>Salvar Modelo STL</string>
           </property>
           <property name="filter">
            <string>Arquivos STL (*.stl)</string>
           </property>
           <property name="storageMode">
            <enum>QgsFileWidget::SaveFile</enum>
           </property>
          </widget>
         </item>
        </layout>
       </item>
       <item>
        <spacer name="verticalSpacer">
         <property name="orientation">
          <enum>Qt::Vertical</enum>
         </property>
         <property name="sizeHint" stdset="0">
          <size>
           <width>20</width>
           <height>150</height>
          </size>
         </property>
        </spacer>
       </item>
       <item>
        <widget class="QProgressBar" name="mProgressBar">
         <property name="value">
          <number>0</number>
         </property>
         <property name="alignment">
          <set>Qt::AlignCenter</set>
         </property>
        </widget>
       </item>
       <item>
        <widget class="QPushButton" name="mGenerateButton">
         <property name="minimumSize">
          <size>
           <width>0</width>
           <height>45</height>
          </size>
         </property>
         <property name="font">
          <font>
           <weight>75</weight>
           <bold>true</bold>
          </font>
         </property>
         <property name="text">
          <string>GERAR MODELO 3D TÁTIL (STL)</string>
         </property>
        </widget>
       </item>
      </layout>
     </widget>
     <widget class="QWidget" name="tabAbout">
      <attribute name="title">
       <string>4. Sobre</string>
      </attribute>
      <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="verticalLayout_6">
       <item>
        <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="horizontalLayout_logo">
          <item>
           <spacer name="horizontalSpacer_left">
            <property name="orientation">
             <enum>Qt::Horizontal</enum>
            </property>
            <property name="sizeHint" stdset="0">
             <size>
              <width>20</width>
              <height>20</height>
             </size>
            </property>
           </spacer>
          </item>
          <item>
           <widget class="QLabel" name="labelLogo">
            <property name="minimumSize">
             <size>
              <width>240</width>
              <height>88</height>
             </size>
            </property>
            <property name="maximumSize">
             <size>
              <width>240</width>
              <height>88</height>
             </size>
            </property>
            <property name="text">
             <string/>
            </property>
            <property name="scaledContents">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="alignment">
             <set>Qt::AlignCenter</set>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item>
           <spacer name="horizontalSpacer_middle">
            <property name="orientation">
             <enum>Qt::Horizontal</enum>
            </property>
            <property name="sizeHint" stdset="0">
             <size>
              <width>30</width>
              <height>20</height>
             </size>
            </property>
           </spacer>
          </item>
          <item>
           <widget class="QLabel" name="labelLogoAnthropic">
            <property name="minimumSize">
             <size>
              <width>88</width>
              <height>88</height>
             </size>
            </property>
            <property name="maximumSize">
             <size>
              <width>88</width>
              <height>88</height>
             </size>
            </property>
            <property name="text">
             <string/>
            </property>
            <property name="scaledContents">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="alignment">
             <set>Qt::AlignCenter</set>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item>
           <spacer name="horizontalSpacer_right">
            <property name="orientation">
             <enum>Qt::Horizontal</enum>
            </property>
            <property name="sizeHint" stdset="0">
             <size>
              <width>20</width>
              <height>20</height>
             </size>
            </property>
           </spacer>
          </item>
        </layout>
       </item>
       <item>
        <widget class="QLabel" name="labelAboutTitle">
         <property name="font">
          <font>
           <pointsize>12</pointsize>
           <weight>75</weight>
           <bold>true</bold>
          </font>
         </property>
         <property name="text">
          <string>DEM to Tactile 3D — Geolab / AnthropicGeo</string>
         </property>
         <property name="alignment">
          <set>Qt::AlignCenter</set>
         </property>
        </widget>
       </item>
       <item>
                 <widget class="QLabel" name="labelAboutDesc">
          <property name="text">
           <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:8px;&quot;&gt;Este complemento foi desenvolvido pelo &lt;b&gt;Geolab&lt;/b&gt; (Laboratório de Geoprocessamento da UDESC, Câmpus do Itacorubi - Florianópolis, do Departamento de Geografia) em parceria com a &lt;b&gt;AnthropicGeo&lt;/b&gt;, uma startup focada em soluções geotecnológicas, nascida a partir deste laboratório.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:8px;&quot;&gt;O principal objetivo do plugin é &lt;b&gt;ajudar no ensino da geografia física&lt;/b&gt; e proporcionar uma rica &lt;b&gt;exploração sensorial tridimensional através de prototipagens táteis&lt;/b&gt;, convertendo Modelos Digitais de Elevação (MDE/raster) e dados vetoriais (como trilhas, hidrografia e limites) em maquetes físicas tridimensionais (STL) perfeitamente sólidas e prontas para impressão 3D.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:8px;&quot;&gt;Ao esculpir e extrudar de forma convexa e arredondada as trilhas e caminhos, ou deprimir de forma plana e nítida as massas d'água, o modelo resultante gera geometrias fechadas e manifold, otimizadas para fatiamento e impressão 3D, com fidelidade topológica ao dado de origem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin-top:12px; color:#00c853;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;Processamento geoespacial aplicado à manufatura aditiva.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
          </property>
          <property name="wordWrap">
           <bool>true</bool>
          </property>
         </widget>
       </item>
       <item>
        <spacer name="verticalSpacer_about">
         <property name="orientation">
          <enum>Qt::Vertical</enum>
         </property>
         <property name="sizeHint" stdset="0">
          <size>
           <width>20</width>
           <height>40</height>
          </size>
         </property>
        </spacer>
       </item>
      </layout>
     </widget>
    </widget>
   </item>
   <item>
    <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="horizontalLayout">
     <item>
